nodes.Entity
id	label	inferred	assumption
Creative	Creative	false	Master source: adcreatives. One row per Meta creative_id. Holds image/video assets, narrative copy, Instagram actor, Shopify product_set linkage. Cross-format attributes (link/video/template) are unioned at CDM stage.
CreativeVariant	CreativeVariant	false	Multi-asset DCO variants. Materialized by unioning 8 child tables (bodies/titles/descriptions/images/videos/ctas/ad_formats/link_urls) with a variant_kind discriminator. Identified positionally — Meta does not expose stable variant IDs.
CreativeProductRef	CreativeProductRef	false	Shopify catalog references on a creative. Materialized from onsite_destinations + retailer_item_ids. ref_kind discriminator separates single-product vs. collection vs. retailer_item.
CreativeFeatureFlag	CreativeFeatureFlag	false	Long-form view of the ~33 degrees_of_freedom_spec__creative_features_spec__*__enroll_status columns. Requires column→row unpivot in create-transformation.
AdPerformance	AdPerformance	false	Daily ad-level fact at (ad_id, date, device_platform) grain. All numeric metrics typed as text in source — must cast to numeric in CDM.
ConversionEvent	ConversionEvent	false	Per-action-type events joined from ads_insights__actions and ads_insights__action_values on (parent_id, action_type) so each row carries both count and value.
AttributedROAS	AttributedROAS	false	Per-action-type ROAS at attribution-window grain. value is a RATIO (revenue/spend) — must NOT sum-aggregate; recompute as SUM(rev)/NULLIF(SUM(spend),0).
Ad	Ad	false	Denormalized dim derived from DISTINCT(ad_id, ad_name) on ads_insights. Bridge to Creative is MISSING — requires /ads endpoint to add creative_id.
AdSet	AdSet	false	Denormalized dim from ads_insights. No targeting/budget/schedule attributes available without /adsets endpoint.
Campaign	Campaign	false	Denormalized dim from ads_insights. No objective/budget/status attributes available without /campaigns endpoint.
AdAccount	AdAccount	false	Denormalized dim from (account_id, account_name) on ads_insights and adcreatives.

