nodes.SemanticGap
concept	use_case	note
Ad↔Creative bridge	creative-level performance attribution	No creative_id on ads_insights and no /ads endpoint pulled. Recommend /new-endpoint to add /{ad_account}/ads with fields=id,creative{id},adset_id,campaign_id,status,effective_status. Without this, AdPerformance cannot join to Creative — only to denormalized ad_id/ad_name.
Campaign objective/budget	ad performance analysis	ads_insights only carries (campaign_id, campaign_name). Objective, daily_budget, lifetime_budget, status, start_time/stop_time require /campaigns endpoint.
AdSet targeting/budget/schedule	ad performance analysis	Similar to Campaign — /adsets endpoint needed for targeting_spec, budget, optimization_goal, billing_event.
Shopify product metadata	product-level creative attribution	CreativeProductRef carries product_id but no name, sku, price, inventory, product_type. Requires Shopify ingestion pipeline.
CreativeVariant performance	creative analysis	Meta does not expose per-variant impressions/clicks/spend in ads_insights. Variant-level performance attribution is not derivable from this pipeline alone.
